---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '@components/Hero.astro';
import Section from '@components/Section.astro';
import Button from '@components/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="General Information"
  description="Important information about Fox Mortuary Services including death certificate preparation, transportation requirements, and professional standards."
>
  <Hero
    title="General Information"
    subtitle="Important details for funeral homes we serve"
    height="medium"
  />

  <Section padding="large">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-forest-800 mb-6">
          About Our Services
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Fox Mortuary Services, LLC is a licensed funeral trade establishment based in
          Wauseon, Ohio. We provide comprehensive professional services to funeral homes
          throughout Northwest Ohio, Southern Michigan, and Northeast Indiana.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gold-50 border-l-4 border-gold-500 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-forest-800 mb-3">
            Important Notice
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Fox Mortuary Services works exclusively with funeral homes and funeral industry
            professionals. We do not provide services directly to the general public. If you
            are seeking funeral services for a loved one, please contact a local funeral home.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-forest-800 mt-12 mb-6">
          Professional Standards
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          All services provided by Fox Mortuary Services meet or exceed industry standards
          and Ohio state licensing requirements. Our team maintains active memberships in
          professional organizations including:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-8">
          <li>American Society of Embalmers</li>
          <li>Ohio Embalmers Association</li>
          <li>Chamber of Commerce</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-forest-800 mt-12 mb-6">
          Death Certificate Information
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We provide prompt death certificate and document preparation services to support
          funeral homes in their administrative responsibilities. Our experienced staff
          ensures accuracy and timely filing of all required documentation.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Proper documentation is essential for funeral homes to serve families effectively.
          We work closely with funeral directors to ensure all paperwork is completed
          correctly and submitted in a timely manner.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-forest-800 mt-12 mb-6">
          Transportation Services
        </h2>
        <div class="bg-forest-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Fox Mortuary Services provides comprehensive transportation services including:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-gold-600 mr-3 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Professional removal services throughout our tri-state service area</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-gold-600 mr-3 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Overland transportation for local and regional needs</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-gold-600 mr-3 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Domestic shipping for out-of-state transfers</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-gold-600 mr-3 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>International shipping as a known shipper</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-forest-800 mt-12 mb-6">
          Facilities
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Our Ohio-licensed facilities are equipped to handle all aspects of embalming,
          preparation, and restoration. We also provide on-site services at funeral homes
          when needed.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          All work is performed by our owner and full-time staff, ensuring consistent quality
          and professional care. This personal commitment sets us apart from other service
          providers in the region.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-forest-800 mt-12 mb-6">
          Service Philosophy
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We understand that funeral service by its very nature is as varied as the
          individuals served in each community. Our experience of over 30 years has taught
          us to adapt to the unique needs of each funeral home while maintaining consistent
          professional standards.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          The trust that funeral homes place in Fox Mortuary Services is something we take
          seriously. Every service we provide is performed with respect, dignity, and
          attention to detail.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-forest-700 p-8 rounded-lg mt-12">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-forest-800 mb-4 text-center">
            Questions or Need More Information?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-center mb-6">
            We're available 24/7 to answer your questions and discuss how we can support
            your funeral home.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <Button href="/contact/" variant="primary" size="large">
              Contact Us
            </Button>
            <Button href="/services/" variant="outline" size="large">
              View Our Services
            </Button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
